items.title: Longtime Iowa federal judge dies at 78 after more than 26 years on the bench
items.description: Robert Pratt, who served as an Iowa federal judge for more than 26 years, died Wednesday at 78 after suffering cardiac arrest while at a gym.

items.title: Illegal immigrant in Florida charged with arson, felony criminal mischief, sheriff says
